dmca.title: Visivites Domain Holder to Knock It Off
dmca.body:
Dear Vitamin Health:
 
VISIVITE is a United States registered trademark of Vitamin Science Inc.
 
You have fraudently and intentionally registered the domain name, VISIVITES.COM.
 
Please advise us as to how you intend to transfer this registration no later than November 5, 2003. If we have not heard from you by then, we will instigate legal recourse seeking financial damages.
 
[Private], President
Vitamin Science Inc
PO Box 1128
Huntington NY 11743
 
Cc: [Private], Esq
